rows.label: bf11450100_0010
rows.name: Since then, I haven't seen him.

rows.label: bf11450100_0020
rows.name:
I heard he went climbing up the World Tree
not long after.

rows.label: bf11450100_0030
rows.name: And brought divine revelations back with him...

rows.label: bf11450100_0040
rows.name: You mean...

rows.label: bf11450100_0050
rows.name: The Grail, Metsu.

rows.label: bf11450100_0060
rows.name: But... What kind of a revelation is this?

rows.label: bf11450100_0070
rows.name: What kind of salvation?

rows.label: bf11450100_0080
rows.name: Could anyone call THIS salvation...?

rows.label: bf11450100_0085
rows.name: His hope caused this...

rows.label: bf11450100_0090
rows.name: Or...his despair.

rows.label: bf11450100_0100
rows.name: Despair...?

rows.label: bf11450100_0110
rows.name:
How about you, then?
You're from the same stock.

rows.label: bf11450100_0120
rows.name: I don't know what you're talking about.

rows.label: bf11450100_0130
rows.name:
I'm just following this guy since
he woke me up, and that's basically it.

rows.label: bf11450100_0140
rows.name: I have no particular interest in this world or its future.

rows.label: bf11450100_0150
rows.name: And Metsu himself?

rows.label: bf11450100_0160
rows.name: His thoughts I'm especially uninterested in.

rows.label: bf11450100_0165
rows.name: We've never even met.

rows.label: bf11450100_0170
rows.name: Please, don't mistake her.

rows.label: bf11450100_0175
rows.name: Despite the attitude, she's a good kid.

rows.label: bf11450100_0180
rows.name: The hell is with that tone?

rows.label: bf11450100_0185
rows.name: Where do you get off acting all parental?

rows.label: bf11450100_0190
rows.name: Hahaha! Oh, come on.

rows.label: bf11450100_0195
rows.name:
I woke you up, I make sure you
get enough to eat...

rows.label: bf11450100_0200
rows.name: Wha-?

rows.label: bf11450100_0210
rows.name:
Cloud Sea Crab Sticks are tasty, aren't they?
You're very welcome.

rows.label: bf11450100_0220
rows.name:
Although I don't think I'd have 
managed to eat six myself.

rows.label: bf11450100_0230
rows.name: What? You counted?!

rows.label: bf11450100_0240
rows.name: I don't know where you put all that.

rows.label: bf11450100_0250
rows.name: I'm the Grail! I need all the fuel I can get!

rows.label: bf11450100_0260
rows.name: Hey!

rows.label: bf11450100_0270
rows.name: You're too easy to sneak up on.

rows.label: bf11450100_0275
rows.name: Where're MY extra rations?

rows.label: bf11450100_0280
rows.name: You little...

rows.label: bf11450100_0290
rows.name:
Hehehe!
The Grail, bested by a little kid! Hehehehe!

rows.label: bf11450100_0300
rows.name: Milt! Get back here!

rows.label: bf11450100_0310
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Heh.

rows.label: bf11450100_0320
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf11450100_0330
rows.name: Y'know... If God really does exist,

rows.label: bf11450100_0340
rows.name: I'd quite like to meet him.

rows.label: bf11450100_0350
rows.name: Salvation, huh?
